casebody.data:
COUNTY OF MAUI, HAWAII, petitioner,
v.
HAWAII WILDLIFE FUND, et al. No. 18-260. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 3, 2018.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. The Solicitor General is invited to file a brief in this case expressing the views of the United States on or before 4 p.m., Friday, January 4, 2019.
